casebody.data:
JACK RUBENSTEIN, PROSECUTOR, v. GEORGE P. NIMMO, SHERIFF. CLARENCE MILLER, PROSECUTOR, v. GEORGE P. NIMMO, SHERIFF. Argued April 20, 1926 Decided May 8, 1926.

Before Justice Parker.

I conclude that on the face of the papers before me, these men are not legally charged with a criminal offense; they will, accordingly, be discharged and the bail exonerated.
